text: Giulia Molinaro (born 23 July 1990) is an Italian professional golfer. Molinaro played her college golf at Arizona State University. Molinaro played on the Symetra Tour in 2013, winning one event, finishing second on the money list, and earning Rookie of the Year honors. Her second place finished earned her an LPGA Tour card for 2014. After making only 8 cuts in 18 events and finishing 114th on the money list in 2014, she was back on the Symetra Tour in 2015. Shew again finished second on the money list and returned to the LPGA Tour in 2016.
